Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Staff, Student

    public abstract class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    What is a person? Person is made in the image of God and are unrelated to animals. A person nature reflects some of God's attributes but in a limited way. A person can be anything they wanted to be as long as God is allowed to do so. A staff in NTU? A politician? Child of god, be whatever you wanted to be.
